is-ff = FF.âˆˆR

ff-map : {ً‌“¤ ً‌“¥ : Level} â†’ Type ً‌“¤ â†’ Type ً‌“¥ â†’ Type (ً‌“ک âٹ” ً‌“¤ âٹ” ً‌“¥)
ff-map A B = خ£[ f âˆ¶ (A â†’ B)] is-ff f

